c: 17
v: 100
t: "Nabiyow! ama korosuk ixxic: isin yi Rabbih rizqhii kee niqmootah kadnoonik tu amlakuk suginnitoonuy toysa gabâ gibdah tet abbaxuk teneeniih sinnik kalih marah tu teetik acayuk mananton nek ambaxelê meesih, seehadayti yakkay maaluk kay gabal taniimil kaxxa gabâ gibdali yekke, Yalli iimaanat dacrise mara akke waytek"